ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
SubjectTransfer of Duties Order
PrecisOrder (1) transferring from the Department of Industry to the Federal Economic Development Agency for Northern Ontario the control and supervision of that portion of the federal public administration in the Department of Industry known as the Federal Economic Development Initiative for Northern Ontario; and (2) ordering the Minister of Economic Development and Official Languages to preside over the Federal Economic Development Agency for Northern Ontario.
